replyContent:
Hello!
The weather in YoWindow and outside the window may be different for some reason.
- The nearest meteorological station is far away.
- Weather is measured at intervals of up to 40 minutes.
You can try changing the weather source.

Dear Rob,
you need to follow these steps to set your location as home (the default one).
- Tap location name at the top of YoWindow screen to open locations list.
- Find your place in the list and tap its menu (3 dots) button.
- In the menu choose "Set As Home".
This will make your location the default one.
